{"tid":1367150,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我地愛香港","createTime":"2019-07-26T07:22:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T07:22:06.000Z","uid":278606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d9e320552a9f27e95a4903926d073138c084fda9","tid":1367150,"uid":278606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"最近有人問我點解咁愛香港，鍾意香港啲乜嘢。之前都有人問過，有人答廣東話、發展程度、經濟水平、司法獨立、自由<del>民主</del>......<br />\n<br />\n大家嘅答案係啲乜嘢？對我嚟講最完美嘅答案係<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">因為嗰度有香港人啊，屌你老母</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有冇同我一樣嘅感覺，當我雙腳踏足係夏愨道，同其他手足共進退嘅時候，我就知道我係一個香港人，永遠都係。<br />\n<br />\n大家都分享下自己仲鍾意香港啲乜嘢<br />\n同埋<br />\n聽日食老婆餅小心d<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"}]}